# ==============================================================================
# .dockerignore — WebVella ERP Microservices
# ==============================================================================
# Excludes unnecessary files from the Docker build context to reduce image size
# and build time. This file is critical for services using 'COPY . .' in their
# Dockerfiles, preventing .git, build artifacts, tests, and documentation from
# being copied into intermediate build stages.
#
# Per AAP Section 0.4.1 and Docker best practices.
# ==============================================================================

# --- Version Control ---
.git
.gitattributes
.gitignore
.github

# --- IDE / Editor Files ---
.vs
.vscode
.idea
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docuser

# --- Build Artifacts ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/

# --- NuGet ---
**/packages/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

# --- Test Projects ---
tests/

# --- Documentation ---
docs/
*.md
!README.md

# --- Docker (prevent recursive context) ---
**/Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore

# --- Infrastructure Scripts (not needed in app images) ---
infrastructure/

# --- LocalStack Data (persistent state volume) ---
localstack-data/

# --- NuGet Packaging ---
create-nuget-pkgs.bat
*.nuspec

# --- License and Legal ---
LICENSE.txt
LIBRARIES.md

# --- Legacy Monolith Site Hosts (not part of microservices) ---
WebVella.Erp.Site/
WebVella.Erp.Site.Sdk/
WebVella.Erp.Site.Next/
WebVella.Erp.Site.Project/
WebVella.Erp.Site.Mail/
WebVella.Erp.Site.Crm/
WebVella.Erp.Site.MicrosoftCDM/

# --- Legacy Console App ---
WebVella.Erp.ConsoleApp/

# --- WebAssembly (out of scope per AAP 0.3.2) ---
WebVella.Erp.WebAssembly/

# --- Temporary Files ---
*.tmp
*.temp
*.log
*.swp
*~
blitzy_adhoc_test_*

# --- OS Files ---
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
